no-new-object.description:
Description

This rule disallows calling theObjectconstructor withnew.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-new-object: "error"*/

var myObject = new Object();

new Object();

var foo = new Object("foo");

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-new-object: "error"*/

var myObject = new CustomObject();

var myObject = {};

var Object = function Object() {};
new Object();

var foo = Object("foo");
